{"tid":1299272,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"撤回同壽終正寢 兩個意思黎 唔好再混淆","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:48.000Z","uid":31542,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2854bbe31f9e7184dc2892dfb3251b6adcca8d","tid":1299272,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"壽終正寢：比喻事物的滅亡。<br />\n<br />\n撤回：表示已成立但尚未受到拘束時，意思表示之表意人將所發出的意思表示予以收回的意思通知。<br />\n<br />\n根本兩樣野黎 唔好再比三毛搞分化啦<br />\n<br />\n林奠又話今日講撤回<br />\n三個月後都可以照樣重推出黎<br />\n但你到時係要第一步重新黎過呀麻<br />\n你試下今日講撤回 三個月後恢復二讀<br />\n到時我實破產都要司法覆核收你皮<br />\n<br />\n唔好再比人混淆啦香港人"},{"pid":"d42d608edde93e8e3a44db6f49578d03ec92ea10","tid":1299272,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fab4965356bcf36f3cfe71696316eb061f0402","tid":1299272,"uid":260806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"造句：請問林鄭月娥幾時壽終正寢？"},{"pid":"38237aeea0cd2198ad7e4863f1d000cba7097743","tid":1299272,"uid":48379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"重點係落唔到立法會到<br />\n<br />\n立法會只有「撤回, withdrawal」同「押後, postpones」呢兩個optional<br />\n其他字都係冇立法會既效力  好多廢中廢老都唔識"},{"pid":"9dd1223c4731d715fd2e10a4adaf2e947e0ffb74","tid":1299272,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6a6ceaadc454e343e119b2488ffdc230edab026","tid":1299272,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"還在玩「語言偽術」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces